</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> uns hat fürgelegt fraw Cristein die
                        Wildensteinerin, unser burgerin, wie daz sie Görg Gotsman,
                                    <add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> diener</add>, an
                                <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan> czehenden czu Sleiffhawsen und
                        Tobernrewte irre und enge und ir das ir <add>mit gewalt</add> davon nem und
                        hinweg für. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> diener durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        willen daran weysen wöllet, daz er die <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin an dem iren ungehindert lasse und,
                        waz <add>er</add> ir genomen hab, daz er ir das widergeb. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>gned<ex>ig,</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> biten wir <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
                        wider.</ab>
</div>
